title: Producer Eddie Sings The National Anthem + John Michael Montgomery Stops By
itunes:title: Producer Eddie Sings The National Anthem + John Michael Montgomery Stops By
description:
The show recaps Eddie’s performance of the National Anthem at last night’s Sounds baseball game. Also, John Michael Montgomery stops by for the Friday Morning Conversation.
